description: Its been 2 years since this girls have met on the US mats. Ariel has had a lot of down time from knee surgery and running the greatest wrestling site on the planet. Bella has been a regular on US and has been improving every day. Today was supposed to be the title bout between Darling and Bella but it was delayed. Ariel Steps in very last minute with no preparation to take on Bella. Bella could have the advantage here.
title: Bella Rossi Takes on Ariel X for exhibition match up
